#{{note|a}} Queen Elizabeth took the title Queen Elizabeth the Queen Mother on the death of her husband [[George VI of the United Kingdom|King George VI]] and accession to the throne of her daughter [[Queen Elizabeth II of the United Kingdom|Queen Elizabeth II]].

